	<entry guid="5aa4268515e1ba8de6049a9cf0f59229" filename="Design" title="Design" content="&amp;lt;h1&amp;gt;Design&amp;lt;/h1&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;What makes Sitemagic CMS shine is not just its ease of use, although we know our users love that. What makes Sitemagic stand out is its built-in Designer that lets us create new beautiful designs in minutes, or customize existing designs in seconds.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;With Sitemagic CMS &amp;lt;em&amp;gt;you&amp;lt;/em&amp;gt; can be a professionel web designer.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Here is a few screenshots of some of the design templates that ships with Sitemagic CMS.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;table class=&amp;quot;SMPagesFluidGridStack900&amp;quot; border=&amp;quot;0&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;tbody&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;tr&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;td style=&amp;quot;padding: 1.25em;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;img title=&amp;quot;/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-About.jpeg&amp;quot; src=&amp;quot;files/images/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-About.jpeg&amp;quot; alt=&amp;quot;/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-About.jpeg&amp;quot; width=&amp;quot;100%&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;td style=&amp;quot;padding: 1.25em;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;img title=&amp;quot;/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-Listings.jpeg&amp;quot; src=&amp;quot;files/images/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-Listings.jpeg&amp;quot; alt=&amp;quot;/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-Listings.jpeg&amp;quot; width=&amp;quot;100%&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;/tr&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;tr&amp;gt;&#13;&#10;&amp;lt;td style=&amp;quot;padding: 1.25em;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;img title=&amp;quot;/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-InteriorDesign.jpeg&amp;quot; src=&amp;quot;files/images/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-InteriorDesign.jpeg&amp;quot; alt=&amp;quot;/Sunrise2/ScreenShots/RealEstate-InteriorDesign.jpeg&amp;quot; width=&amp;quot;100%